# Gdblib Installation instructions

## Software requirements
* For the moment I have only tested gdblib in Linux 3.4.2
* Gdb 7.4, but any gdb with MI interface should work
* Python 2.6
* Gnu Make for testing purposes
* Python coverage for coverage purposes http://nedbatchelder.com/code/coverage/

### The following instructions are supposed to be executed in the gdblib parent source code folder

## Howto build gdblib
python2 setup.py build

## Howto install gdblib
python2 setup.py install 

## Howto install in a specific location
python2 setup.py install --prefix=/usr

## Howto test gdblib
python2 setup.py test

## Howto generate test coverage
python2 setup.py coverage
